Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------OPCN1-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------EDCN1-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------PREV-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.20,0:00:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很正常啊 冬天來海邊當然冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.72,0:00:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是學長自己說要來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.02,0:00:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣冷下去會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.31,0:00:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓我暖和下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.55,0:00:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖和？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七咲的身體真暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這就是帶我來海邊的目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天這麼難得 有什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.12,0:00:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時在學校幾乎都見不上面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我平時都要去上高考補習班
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七咲則是有游泳部部長的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到家還要做家務
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次的平安夜約會真令人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.67,0:00:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:00:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後過了快一年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又快到聖誕節的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年過得真高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.95,0:01:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那個溫泉出現山鹿的異常繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.03,0:01:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在連山也進不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年得找其他地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長 今年的平安夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會考上大學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為一個配得上七咲的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個令人不放心的學長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:55.87,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}邂逅的那一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:02:02.31,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}察覺到的朦朧情感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.96,0:02:10.13,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}直至已化為確信的今日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:14.69,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}那份感覺仍否在你心中？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:16.52,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}全因有你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:19.52,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:23.57,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}心湖泛起陣陣漣漪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:29.05,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此刻與你一同邁步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:32.11,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:36.09,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}聆聽心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:37.60,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:41.63,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去感受內心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.65,0:02:46.93,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}宛如夢幻的時間流淌著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:54.71,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}渴望凝望你雙眸中的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:58.71,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:02.69,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}聆聽心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:04.30,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:10.68,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去感受內心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小逢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 美也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在睡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚好像複習到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正打呼嚕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都過來幫我叫他起床 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小事而已 別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是喜歡做才做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有小逢做女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥真是幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長該起床了 學長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要遲到了 趕快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想睡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:03:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間沒剩多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天打算翹課了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不起床就把你從被子裡拉出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:27.26,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,650)\pos(320,260)\t(0,800,\fs14)}七咲 逢篇\N\N前篇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:27.26,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,650)\pos(320,260)\t(0,800,\fs14)}七咲 逢篇\N\N前篇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:27.26,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,650)\pos(319,295)\fs17\t(0,800,\fs16)}逞 強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:27.26,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,650)\pos(319,295)\fs17\t(0,800,\fs16)}逞 強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽美也說你昨晚很晚才睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有點拼過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像應考生的熱情被瞬間點燃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不要太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 部長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是一清早就打得火熱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 哥們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了梅原 突然之間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的高中三年就成一片灰色了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都想在聖誕之前交到女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既有妹妹又有女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能幫上我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我隨便介紹個女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在只能靠你了 哥們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}別這樣 冷靜點 梅原
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不答應我的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了 哥們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}幫幫可憐的我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}快放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:05:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絢辻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是來圖書室複習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天的補習班暫停了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也想換下環境
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絢辻你也來這邊複習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 你不是拿到保送名額了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是這樣 但已經養成習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不學習的話就渾身不自在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能把學習養成習慣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道這樣是好還是壞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了 橘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是時候回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了這麼多一年級女生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部員還挺多的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點就忘了來這的目的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:07:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家注意好換氣和起跳的時機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有部長的風範了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像去年的塚原學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還敢說「怎麼？」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前也說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女子游泳部使用泳池時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生是禁止入內的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 當然沒忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼還進來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了吧 部長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一到這個時間 部長就常往門口那邊看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反 反省了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團活動時再也不要進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團活動時再也不會進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好反省
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦 小逢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這麼容易就原諒他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美 美也
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今年加入了游泳部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒聽過這事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒告訴過你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告訴你才比較有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如這次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七咲當然是早就知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美也叫我別說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先別說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能輕易就原諒他呢 小逢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥他不單只看你一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還偷笑著看其他人的泳裝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有偷笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿嘴謊話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你怎麼擺出一副色迷迷的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鉤了吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 這是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 聽我解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.53,0:09:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個色學長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我真的是為了見七咲才去泳池的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天補習班暫停了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,0:09:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想著能跟你一起放學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…只是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七咲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但條件是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為懲罰 接下來要陪我去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近的超市今天有大減價
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每人限購兩板雞蛋和一盒牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的懲罰 我很願意接受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再敢來偷看就絕不原諒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七咲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.47,0:10:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 吵醒你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幫我蓋上被子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:10:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別起來了 就這麼躺著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七咲你怎麼到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本打算找學長一起吃午飯的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽美也說你昨晚複習到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 說起美也我想起一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她小時候經常睡在爸爸的肚子上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的弟弟郁夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我一唱搖籃曲他很快就會睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒睡在肚子上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是剛剛才想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:11:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能睡在七咲的肚子上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著你唱搖籃曲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定能睡得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.21,0:12:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人看見了多不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 床的周圍都有簾子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它拉上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定能緩解學習上的疲勞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 為什麼要蓋住我的眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我會害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶貝 寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶貝聽話 快入睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶貝是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願你睡得安穩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻山越嶺  出遠門了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.76,0:14:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的睡得很安穩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁夫 做完作業之後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好明天的準備就早點睡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起來郁夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡在被爐裡會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕節要去哪裡玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要盡快跟學長商量才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不懂你為什麼突然要跟我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的 上週補習班舉行了模考
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成績在昨天發下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:15:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很差嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多差？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只算補習班的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排名也是從下往上數會比較快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案基本都對了 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是填塗的時候填錯位了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是低級的錯誤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顏面無存
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不需要因這點事而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.14,0:15:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次注意些就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不是為了這事而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是為了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的補習班實行斯巴達式的培訓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 對於模考成績差的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須參加遲些的合宿補習
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而合宿則是在12月23日開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 我也對補習班的老師說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是填塗的時候填錯位而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案基本都對了就放我一馬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.07,0:16:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後她就說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果正式考試時犯了同樣的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也打算這樣找藉口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說要住進有恐怖宿管在的宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 幾乎是完全的監禁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從早上5點自習到晚上睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無休息時間一直學習
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我在創設祭之後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要參加女子游泳部的雜燴攤慶功宴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還擔心著有沒有時間去約會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.68,0:16:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身為部長怎能缺席呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請不要放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我遲些一定會補償你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我會期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.27,0:17:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長在合宿時一定要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 今年的創設祭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們班決定出演戲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把出演角色和幕後人員先分配好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有提議的人請舉手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼會說出那種話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週就要開始晨練備戰年初的大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有創設祭的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越難見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:17:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小逢想演什麼角色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有雜燴攤的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這邊也很想參加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆兩邊都參加玩個痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小逢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長就要參加合宿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只能為他準備一張毛毯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還可以吧 合宿時也用得上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然提早了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是我為了給學長打氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而準備的聖誕禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕約會的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰喜歡去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.58,0:20:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首選一定是港口塔樓之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然少不了遊樂場和電影院還有卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為聖誕約會適合看電影的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會這麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海洋館會舉辦聖誕節的特備燈會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夢幻般夜幕的映襯下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和心愛的人身處海洋館中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人獨處渡過一個平安夜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說是完全沉醉於環境氣氛當中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有男生不著迷的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單是想像就足以令人心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得先找個男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 小逢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.19,0:20:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥昨晚被人帶去合宿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是還沒到時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:20:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成績特別差的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.12,0:21:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿時間要比其他人早開始晚結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補習班的人突然找上門來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把哥哥給帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把這件事告訴七咲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小逢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.17,0:21:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在有好好地學習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長他正在努力備考
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也必須忍耐才行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:34.56,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}清晨傳來腳踏車的清脆鈴聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:40.15,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}彷彿告訴著我時間逐漸流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.93,0:22:46.11,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}盼望把這顆熾熱的心交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:51.41,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}並許下對你一心一意的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.61,0:23:03.32,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}兩手緊握著華美絢麗的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.64,0:23:09.47,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我此刻最想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.06,0:23:14.38,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}於深秋落葉時深呼吸一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:22.02,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}嘴裡吐出的卻是絲絲的嘆息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.31,0:23:29.46,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}現在只希望你能聽我說一句
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.71,0:23:32.52,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:36.44,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}這便是我的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.88,0:23:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回預告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.85,0:23:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.61,0:23:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七咲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.30,0:23:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.63,0:23:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安夜撇下你 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.35,0:23:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七咲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.85,0:23:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算獨自一人 我也會好好地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.27,0:23:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長請在遙遠的天邊守護我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.89,0:23:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.01,0:23:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被強迫參加合宿而已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.05,0:24:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.84,0:24:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不要嚇我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.49,0:24:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.02,0:24:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我果然還是會覺得寂寞
